  "notes": "This release contains unreleased alternate recordings from the \"Masada Book of Songs\", which has been released between 1994 and 1997 by DIW, in total 10 CD's. Only one composition (\"Mashav\", track 2-02) has never been published before or afterwards on another release.\n\nRecorded at Avatar and RPM, NYC\nMastered at Hit Factory Mastering, NYC\n\nA project of Hips Road\nⒸⓅ 2005 Tzadik\n",
